TimelineContent.timeline2025Description: Wannan ni ne yau - Co-founder & CEO na LiquidOps, yarjejeniyar bashi da aro ta farko a Arweave & AO. Mun ∆ôaddamar da testnet …óinmu da ∆ôaddamar da adalci.
TimelineContent.timeline2024Description: Wannan shekara ta canza komai. Na sadu da Marton a Cambridge kuma muka ∆ôir∆ôiri Operation Liquidity. Sa'ad da muka ∆ôaddamar da jerin jira, mun kai dala miliyan 2 a cikin alkawura cikin awanni 2 kawai. Ya girma zuwa dala miliyan 55 daga rajista sama da 3,000. Mun tara zagaye na pre-seed na dala 325K kuma mun rabu da Community Labs a matsayin spinout na Fellow na farko.
TimelineContent.timeline2023Description: Na zama Fellow na waje na farko a Community Labs nan da nan bayan zagaye na seed …óinsu. Na mayar da tallafin bincike na don mai da hankali gaba …óaya kan yanayin Arweave. A wannan lokacin, na gina Othent, Oases, subsidise-JS, kuma na yi aiki a AO Ventures. A nan ne na sami mutanena da gaske.
TimelineContent.timeline2022Title: Na shiga Community Labs & na gina aikin farko na
TimelineContent.timeline2022Description: Na ∆ôir∆ôiri dandamali na binciken ma'amaloli na crypto kuma na sami tallafi na dala 100k daga hanyoyin Polkadot da Kusama. Wannan shine lokacin da na koya wa kaina yin code da kyau. Na yi aiki cikakken lokaci akan aikin tare da wasu 'yan kwangila masu zaman kansu da na samu. Yana da gajiya amma yana da ban sha'awa. Har ila yau na shiga Community Labs. Na fara indie hacking daga shagunan kofi maimakon gina VC.
TimelineContent.timeline2021Title: Na shiga Crypto VC daga …óakin kwana na
TimelineContent.timeline2021Description: Na sami horarwa ba tare da biya ba a wani asusun jari hujja na crypto. Na yi aiki watanni 3 ba tare da biya ba kafin su ba ni matsayin mai bincike da aka biya. Na yi aiki a gefen VC da hedge fund.
TimelineContent.timeline2020Title: Saurayi Crypto a Makarantar Wasan kwaikwayo
TimelineContent.timeline2020Description: Yayin da nake Makarantar Wasan kwaikwayo, na fara tashar ilimi ta Crypto TikTok da ke nufin koyar da Gen Z game da Crypto. Farashin ETH dala 201 ne! Ina sayar da tufafi don biyan makarantar Wasan kwaikwayo. Na aika imel zuwa kamfanoni sama da 500 da VCs suna neman horarwa ba tare da biya ba ko kowane aiki a masana'antar. Ina halartar tarurrukan Zoom a filin ajiye motoci na makarantar tare da wayar abokin aji …óina da ke da bayanai yayin da nake kaucewa azuzuwan don gabatar da ra'ayi ga VCs da kasuwanci game da yiwuwar …óaukar aiki na.
